<pb n="0758a" id="T14.0494.0758a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0758a01" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/><head type="no">No. 494</head>
<lb n="0758a02" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><note n="0758001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（佛說）＋阿【明】</note><app n="0758001"><lem wit="【大】">阿</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">佛說阿</rdg></app>難七夢經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0758a03" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator">東晉<note n="0758002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">天竺三藏＝西域沙門【三】【宮】</note><note n="0758002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">天竺三藏＝西域沙門【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0758002"><lem wit="【大】">天竺三藏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">西域沙門</rdg></app>竺曇無蘭譯</byline>
<lb n="0758a04" ed="T"/><div1 type="jing"><p id="pT14p0758a0401">阿難在舍衛國。有七種夢。來問於佛。一者
<lb n="0758a05" ed="T"/><note n="0758003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（夢）＋陂【三】【宮】</note><note n="0758003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（夢）＋陂【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0758003"><lem wit="【大】">陂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">夢陂</rdg></app>池火炎滔天。二者夢日月沒星宿亦沒。三
<lb n="0758a06" ed="T"/>者夢出家比丘。轉在於不淨坑塹之中。在家
<lb n="0758a07" ed="T"/>白衣。登頭而出。四者夢群&CB00337;來觝<note n="0758004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00247;＝突【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0758004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB00247;＝突【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0758004"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00247;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">突</rdg></app>栴檀
<lb n="0758a08" ed="T"/>林<note n="0758005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔怪之〕－【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0758005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔怪之〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0758005"><lem wit="【大】">怪之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>。五者夢頭戴須彌山。不以為重。六
<lb n="0758a09" ed="T"/>者夢大象棄小象。七者夢師子王名華<note n="0758006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">撒＝薩【三】【宮】</note><note n="0758006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">撒＝薩【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0758006"><lem wit="【大】">撒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">薩</rdg></app>頭
<lb n="0758a10" ed="T"/>上。有七毫毛。在地而死。一切禽獸。見故怖
<lb n="0758a11" ed="T"/>畏。後見身中蟲出。然後食之。以此惡夢。來
<lb n="0758a12" ed="T"/>問於佛。佛時在舍衛國普會講堂上。與波斯
<lb n="0758a13" ed="T"/>匿王。說法苦<note n="0758007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">習＝集【三】【宮】</note><note n="0758007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">習＝集【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0758007"><lem wit="【大】">習</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">集</rdg></app>滅得道。為樂見阿難憂色
<lb n="0758a14" ed="T"/>愁苦叵言。佛告阿難。汝於夢者。皆為當來
<lb n="0758a15" ed="T"/>五濁惡世。不損汝也。何為憂色。第一夢陂
<lb n="0758a16" ed="T"/>池火炎滔天者。當來比丘。善心轉少。惡逆
<lb n="0758a17" ed="T"/>熾盛。共相殺害。不可稱計。第二夢<note n="0758008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔者〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0758008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔者〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0758008"><lem wit="【大】">者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>日月
<lb n="0758a18" ed="T"/>沒星宿亦沒。佛泥洹後。一切聲聞。隨佛泥
<lb n="0758a19" ed="T"/>洹不在世。眾生眼滅。第三夢出家比丘。轉
<lb n="0758a20" ed="T"/>在於不淨坑塹之中。在家白衣。登頭出者。當
<lb n="0758a21" ed="T"/>來比丘懷毒嫉&CB00107;。至相殺害。道士斬頭。白
<lb n="0758a22" ed="T"/>衣視之。諫訶不從。死入地獄。白衣精進。死
<lb n="0758a23" ed="T"/>生天上。第四夢者。群&CB00337;來觝<app source="0758004" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00247;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">突</rdg></app>栴檀林<app source="0758005" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">怪
<lb n="0758a24" ed="T"/>之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>者。當來白衣。來入塔寺。誹謗眾僧。求其
<lb n="0758a25" ed="T"/>長短。破塔害僧。第五夢者。頭戴須彌山。不
<lb n="0758a26" ed="T"/>以為重者。佛泥洹後。阿難當為千阿羅漢。出
<lb n="0758a27" ed="T"/>經之師。一句不忘。受悟亦多。不以為重。第
<lb n="0758a28" ed="T"/>六夢者。大象棄小象。將來邪見熾盛。壞我
<lb n="0758a29" ed="T"/>佛法。有德之人。皆隱不現。第七夢師子死
<pb n="0758b" id="T14.0494.0758b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0758b01" ed="T"/>者。佛泥洹後。一千四百七十歲。<note n="0758009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">我＝中【三】【宮】</note><note n="0758009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">我＝中【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0758009"><lem wit="【大】">我</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">中</rdg></app>諸弟子
<lb n="0758b02" ed="T"/>修德之心。一切惡魔不得<note n="0758010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">嬈＝擾【三】【宮】</note><note n="0758010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">嬈＝擾【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0758010"><lem wit="【大】">嬈</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">擾</rdg></app>亂。七毫者七
<lb n="0758b03" ed="T"/>百歲後事。</p></div1>
<lb n="0758b04" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="close"><jhead><note n="0758011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（佛說）＋阿【三】【宮】</note><note n="0758011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（佛說）＋阿【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0758011"><lem wit="【大】">阿</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">佛說阿</rdg></app>難七夢經</jhead></juan>
</body></text></TEI.2>